rows.label: tev025601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Ornella about the people of NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0001
rows.name:
We've had a lot to chew on, that's for damn sure.
First the Earth's demise, then a long, lonely voyage on
the White Whale...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0002
rows.name:
And now, an unknown planet full of indigens and
xenos is trying to wipe us out. They were right when
they called the Exodus a "project." It feels like one![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Some folks are strong enough to stay upbeat, but let's
face itâ€”we're human. Not everyone has been taking
the transition so well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0004
rows.name:
I know it's taken its toll on me. If I didn't have a good
friend like Hope to keep me going, I would have given
up long ago. But hey, here I am![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0005
rows.name:
I'm sure you've got your share of worries as well.
If it ever feels like too much, come talk to me or Hope,
okay? That's what we're here for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0011
rows.name: I noticed that Hope really blossoms around you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0012
rows.name:
Oh, she's all smiles around the rest of us,
but sometimes I think it's just to make us feel better.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0013
rows.name:
But with you, she doesn't seem to try quite so hard.
She just looks more...relaxed, I guess? Maybe because
you're a BLADE and you understand her. I don't know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0014
rows.name:
Either way, I'm glad she has you.
Stick by her for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0019
rows.name:
Hey, Hope. Welcome back! Any injuries?
How are you holding up?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0020
rows.name:
Everything's under control here, so you just focus on
what's on your plate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0021
rows.name:
Thank you, Ornella. I promise I'll take care of
everyone's problems when I get back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0022
rows.name:
I know I'm doubling your workload in the meantime.
I pray you can forgive me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025601_MSG0023
rows.name:
Oh, please. I wouldn't have signed up if I didn't enjoy
the work. Feel free to ride me like a rented mule![ST:wait ]
